Additionally, the paper discusses the placement of computing devices at the edge of the network, which suggests cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as another likely category. The paper also mentions privacy concerns, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as a possible category. Finally, the paper mentions the use of small cameras, which suggests cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as a possible category.
